@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%);
        color: #f0f0f5;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 3rem 1rem;
    }

    .policy-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: auto;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65);
        border-radius: 1rem;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        box-shadow:
            0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
            inset 0 0 15px rgba(255, 213, 79, 0.3);
        line-height: 1.65;
    }

    h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: 900;
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #000;
        color: #ffd54f;
    }

    h2 {
        margin-top: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #ffeb99;
        font-weight: 700;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #ffd54f;
        padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        color: #ddd;
    }

    ul {
        margin-left: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #ccc;
    }

    ul li {
        margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    }

    a {
        color: #ffd54f;
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    a:hover {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 600px) {
        .policy-container {
            padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.3rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="policy-container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>At Bookstore, your privacy is our top priority. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you visit our website or make a purchase.</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address, shipping address, phone number.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit card details and billing address (processed securely via payment gateways).</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information on how you use our website, including pages visited and time spent.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and Tracking:</strong> We use cookies to enhance your experience and gather analytics.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is used to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Process and fulfill your orders securely.</li>
        <li>Communicate with you about your account, orders, and promotions.</li>
        <li>Improve our website and personalize your shopping experience.</li>
        <li>Comply with legal obligations and prevent fraud.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. Our payment processing is handled by trusted third-party providers.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@bookstore.com">privacy@bookstore.com</a>.</p>

    <h2>Cookies Policy</h2>
    <p>Our website uses cookies to offer you a better browsing experience. You can control cookies through your browser settings.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, feel free to <a href="/Home/Contact">contact us</a>.</p>

    <p><em>Last updated: July 2025</em></p>
</div>
